<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="72">New records.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="72">
Montenegro, Skadar Lake area, old stillwater channel near the River 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Crnojevića">Crnojevica</normalizedToken>
and above the village Rijeka 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Crnojevića">Crnojevica</normalizedToken>
, 15 m asl., 
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="42.35495">42°21.297'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="1" value="19.0187">19°01.122' E</geoCoordinate>
, 10.xi.2012, 
